{"tid":1114092,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"因為呢樣野同個best friend 反咗面","createTime":"2019-04-18T09:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T10:37:05.000Z","uid":127018,"like":5,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"98725e80064d2d16741e1ee8987c729c96747867","tid":1114092,"uid":127018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"我同呢個friend 識咗10年<br />\n上星基第一次一齊去日本旅行<br />\nPlan 行程個d我地都好有共識，無咩爭吵<br />\n其實成個trip都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有樣嘢我真係好反感<br />\n佢晚晚臨瞓前都係到開抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭幾晚我都係叫佢細聲d <br />\n話d聲好嘈 我好攰<br />\n佢都有就我 細聲d<br />\n<br />\n到最後一晚，佢又係到睇<br />\n我叫佢細聲d 佢較細聲咗<br />\n但電話聲係細咗 佢嘅笑聲就好大聲<br />\n可能因為我姨媽到嘅關係<br />\n變到好易炆，就不耐煩咁問佢<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你成日睇，真係好好睇咩，可唔可以唔好睇，d聲好嘈。我唔舒服，想早d瞓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔睇就收皮啦，我都較細聲咗，你仲想點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我聽到真係燥咗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你睇你都可以細聲d 或者帶耳機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收皮啦，我都有比酒店錢㗎。你憑咩嘈我？憑咩干涉我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我就無理佢，我有我瞓，佢有佢笑<br />\n<br />\n結果第2日回程時都面阻阻，返到香港我whatsapp佢，佢已讀不回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我地一個friend 話佢尋晚約咗佢食飯時係咁數我，叫人以後唔好同我去旅行<br />\n<br />\n其實我係咪太過份，太過霸道，搞到無咗個friend <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8bb8693a89f60a37d623c9d5fba35517432aa4","tid":1114092,"uid":243550,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:32:03.000Z","msg":"小學雞，大陸喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fd2bfb30434ca5e96ba06ca326a79ba2e1b44e","tid":1114092,"uid":50502,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"兩個人都閪 打和啦"},{"pid":"cd9000b8e404ded0c5d3eae12b69d87b7e7b3035","tid":1114092,"uid":3852,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n你最錯冇數返佢<br />\n以牙還牙, 同全世界講佢用抖音好嘈, 叫fd唔好同佢去旅行"},{"pid":"47b5a3fa13b5014f9d7f334a74fc3ab954dc9d5a","tid":1114092,"uid":14606,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"睇抖音既人重做朋友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39cfbc4cc2c0b363e293f6e8721784832de73b0","tid":1114092,"uid":127018,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"83fd2bfb30434ca5e96ba06ca326a79ba2e1b44e","tid":1114092,"uid":50502,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"兩個人都閪 打和啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:34:23.000Z","msg":"我都知我閪，我返香港都有道歉<br />\n但佢已讀不回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d06c01e59bf495c0cdf69f720023a0fbadb284","tid":1114092,"uid":127018,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"47b5a3fa13b5014f9d7f334a74fc3ab954dc9d5a","tid":1114092,"uid":14606,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"睇抖音既人重做朋友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:35:48.000Z","msg":"佢話佢唔係睇抖音<br />\n佢係開YouTube 睇合集<br />\n所以係睇YouTube <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b082a6a9a1f88f5279cd454fac04dc3a4b8b054","tid":1114092,"uid":238296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"宜個fd可以唔要 俾我打撚左佢好耐"},{"pid":"6a2667ec8583a5050079dd22021292aa016956dc","tid":1114092,"uid":127018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{